::KitKat::

She offered him a seat and took a seat opposite him at the 
table. "What is it that is so urgent?"

DarkMouse::
She pulled her feet off the console and watched on the small panel 
monitor that KitKat and another bot were in the conference room. 
Being a little on the nosey side today, she turned up the microphone 
in the room and listened in on the conversation. She smiled, she was 
having a little fun playing spy. She had no one to tell anything to, 
but it was fun going through the motions.
